This file contains all commands required to deploy and access Apache and NGINX inside the webapps namespace.

ğŸš€ Apply Deployments & Services
kubectl apply -f apache.yaml
kubectl apply -f nginx.yaml
kubectl get deploy,pods,svc -n webapps

ğŸ“¦ Check Deployments
kubectl get deployments -n webapps

ğŸ” Check Pods (Wide View)
