ğŸŒ Check Services
kubectl get svc -n webapps

ğŸ”Œ Port-Forward to Access Apache
kubectl port-forward svc/apache-service -n webapps 8080:80


Access: http://localhost:8080

ğŸ”Œ Port-Forward to Access NGINX
kubectl port-forward svc/nginx-service -n webapps 9090:80


